ctly impact these sectors. This could provide an early signal for regulatory changes or government-backed program shifts affecting your portfolio.', '[{"id":"7d7a39e1-a266-4e1e-b726-25b67524d330","influence":"Unknown","name":"Jack Phan","title":"Data Strategy"}]', '[{"role":"Portfolio Manager, Senior Analyst (Financials/Credit), Head of Research"}]', 'not_started', 'pending', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2026-03-13 02:54:13.576926+00', '2026-03-13 02:54:13.576926+00', '{"coverage_overlap_score":10,"evidence_summary":"Beach Point Capital''s financial services holdings, especially in mortgage finance, can be indirectly influenced by government policies and programs.","product_relevance_score":45,"sector_relevance":["Financials","Mortgage Finance"],"supporting_companies":["VELOCITY FINL INC","FINANCE OF AMERICA COMPAN"]}') ON CONFLICT (id) DO NOTHING;
INSERT INTO campaign_targets (id, campaign_id, client_id, prospect_name, prospect_type, is_existing_client, fit_score, fit_rationale, recommended_approach, recommended_messaging, recommended_contacts, target_personas, status, outreach_status, notes, owner_id, opportunity_id, contacted_at, responded_at, meeting_booked_at, created_at, updated_at, product_fit_analysis) VALUES ('df1dfad1-3776-4d7e-9004-c634c51a778a', '842109f6-9292-4b3a-bda2-0f0ac04dc1ed', '3d2df149-83dc-4c6b-8324-7116eee47d6b', NULL, NULL, 'false', 67, '{"best_persona":"Portfolio Manager, Senior Analyst (Energy/Logistics), Head of Research","evidence_of_fit":"Massar Capital''s portfolio includes holdings in traditional sectors like Energy (Exxon Mobil Corp, 1.57%) and Logistics (UPS), which often involve government contracts for infrastructure, supply chain, and energy resources.","opportunity_type":"new_opportunity","product_relevance_rationale":"Forward-Looking Receivables data can provide Massar Capital with predictive signals on upcoming government contract awards and spending commitments for their holdings in Exxon Mobil and other companies in energy or logistics sectors. This can aid in revenue prediction models and pipeline forecasting for these government-dependent companies.","scores":{"conversion_likelihood":80,"product_relevance":45,"relationship_strength":50,"strategic_fit":80,"timing_signal":70},"why_now":"Active opportunity detected, indicating current engagement and potential interest."}', 'Propose a focused discussion on how Forward-Looking Receivables data can enhance their analysis of energy and logistics companies with government exposure.', 'For your holdings in traditional sectors like Energy (Exxon Mobil) and Logistics, which often secure government contracts, our Forward-Looking Receivables data can offer crucial early insights. This intelligence can enhance your revenue prediction and earnings surprise detection capabilities for these key investments.', '[{"id":"391b1bf8-d946-4249-bfff-b91b57a4251f","influence":"Unknown","name":"Kristoffer Laursen","title":"Senior Quant Strategist"}]', '[{"role":"Portfolio Manager, Senior Analyst (Energy/Logistics), Head of Research"}]', 'not_started', 'pending', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2026-03-13 02:54:13.576926+00', '2026-03-13 02:54:13.576926+00', '{"coverage_overlap_score":51,"evidence_summary":"Massar Capital holds Exxon Mobil and has exposure to logistics, sectors with government contract dependencies.","product_relevance_score":45,"sector_relevance":["Energy","Logistics"],"supporting_companies":["EXXON MOBIL CORP","UPS"]}') ON CONFLICT (id) DO NOTHING;
INSERT INTO campaign_targets (id, campaign_id, client_id, prospect_name, prospect_type, is_existing_client, fit_score, fit_rationale, recommended_approach, recommended_messaging, recommended_contacts, target_personas, status, outreach_status, notes, owner_id, opportunity_id, contacted_at, responded_at, meeting_booked_at, created_at, updated_at, product_fit_analysis) VALUES ('4b61f8e7-3bd5-43a6-abc3-bef3ca24bc2e', '842109f6-9292-4b3a-bda2-0f0ac04dc1ed', 'c7d9e48f-dcc8-4ace-8d74-6115bcebf486', NULL, NULL, 'false', 55, '{"best_persona":"Head of Research, Senior Analyst","evidence_of_fit":"American Securities'' portfolio is heavily skewed towards large-cap technology and consumer discretionary companies, such as Microsoft, Alphabet, Amazon, and Nvidia. There is no direct evidence of significant government contract exposure for these specific holdings in the provided intelligence.","opportunity_type":"new_opportunity","product_relevance_rationale":"While American Securities holds major tech companies, the provided intelligence does not explicitly indicate their reliance on government contracts. Therefore, the direct product relevance for Forward-Looking Receivables is low without further information on their government-facing business segments.","scores":{"conversion_likelihood":90,"product_relevance":0,"relationship_strength":50,"strategic_fit":90,"timing_signal":50},"why_now":"No specific timing signal."}', 'Conduct further research into the government contract exposure of their top holdings or offer a general introductory call to explore potential indirect applications.', 'While your portfolio is concentrated in large-cap tech and consumer discretionary, we are exploring potential indirect applications of our Forward-Looking Receivables data. If any of your holdings, such as Microsoft or Amazon, have significant government-facing business units, our data could provide unique predictive insights into their revenue streams.', '[{"id":"4cb42d35-2500-4ed4-86e1-3993d9e4ac80","influence":"Unknown","name":"Jin Choi","title":"Quantitative Researcher"},{"id":"76ea7772-77f9-4f6c-a082-244e94f4e538","influence":"Unknown","name":"Kajetan Zwieniecki","title":"Quant Researcher"}]', '[{"role":"Head of Research, Senior Analyst"}]', 'not_started', 'pending', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2026-03-13 02:54:13.576926+00', '2026-03-13 02:54:13.576926+00', '{"coverage_overlap_score":0,"evidence_summary":"No direct evidence of government contract exposure for current holdings.","product_relevance_score":0,"sector_relevance":[],"supporting_companies":[]}') ON CONFLICT (id) DO NOTHING;
